sentences: Remi Fischer (born 14 February 1983 in Paris, France) is a French DJ and record producer.
Pretending autorship for recordings such as Discobitch, Club Certified, Closer, and No Tomorrow.
On Aug 25, 2004 Remy offers his services on http://www.macmusic.org/agora/mview.php/lang/en/id/49503
In 2009 Kylian Mash re-used material from a song by Laurent Konrad's band, XXI.
